land, C., Colman, A., Mehta, V., Inter-decadal modulation of the impact of ENSO on Australia (1999) Climate Dyn, 15, pp. 319-324; Qiu, B., Kuroshio Extension variability and forcing of the Pacific decadal oscillations: Responses and potential feed-back (2003) J. Phys. Oceanogr, 33, pp. 2465-2482; Qiu, B., Chen, S., Seasonal modulations in the eddy field of the South Pacific Ocean (2004) J. Phys. Oceanogr, 34, pp. 1515-1527; Qiu, B., Chen, S., Decadal variability in the large-scale sea surface height field of the South Pacific Ocean: Observations and causes (2006) J. Phys. Oceanogr, 36, pp. 1751-1762; Rayner, N.A., Parker, D.E., Horton, E.B., Folland, C.K., Alexander, L.V., Rowell, D.P., Kent, E.C., Kaplan, A., Global analyses of sea surface temperature, sea ice, and night marine air temperature since the late nineteenth century (2003) J. Geophys. Res, 108, p. 4407. , doi:10.1029/2002JD002670; Reid, J., On the total geostrophic circulation of the South Pacific Ocean: Flow patterns, tracers, and transports (1986) Prog. Oceanogr, 39, pp. 263-352; Ridgway, K.R., Dunn, J.R., Mesoscale structure of the mean East Australian Current system and its relationship with topography (2003) Prog. Oceanogr, 56, pp. 189-222; Roemmich, D., Gilson, J., Davis, R., Sutton, P., Wijffels, S., Riser, S., Decadal spinup of the South Pacific subtropical gyre (2007) J. Phys. Oceanogr, 37, pp. 162-173; Rosati, A., Miyakoda, K., A general circulation model for upper ocean circulation (1988) J. Phys. Oceanogr, 18, pp. 1601-1626; Sasaki, H., A series of eddy-resolving ocean simulations in the world ocean: OFES (OGCM for the Earth Simulator) project (2004) Proc. Oceans'04/MTS/IEEE/Techno-Ocean'04, 3, pp. 1535-1541; Sasaki, H., Nonaka, M., Masumoto, Y., Sasai, Y., Uehara, H., Sakuma, H., An eddy-resolving hindcast simulation of the quasi-global ocean from 1950 to 2003 on the Earth Simulator (2007) High Resolution Numerical Modeling of the Atmosphere and Ocean, pp. 157-186. , W. Ohfuchi and K. Hamilt